data.description: Inviting Meadow Park ranch style brings great opportunity!  Enjoy the open living spaces, nicely appointed kitchen & dining area w/ pantry,  large walk in shower, & three main level bedrooms. New AC in '23, newer roof and siding, and appliances only a few years old.  Finished lower level w/ possibility of 4th & 5th bedrooms, & additional bath w/ tub & room for shower.  Oversized 2 car garage, large fenced back yard, concrete pad, & storage shed. Convenient location near all 3 schools, shopping, highways, & Mayo campus.  See it soon!
